graph","text":"28.67","index":19,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"799640ff2d","type":"paragraph","text":"56.851975","index":20,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"3cf1472204","type":"paragraph","text":"60.1646.88","index":21,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"f4483eb532","type":"paragraph","text":"376.53","index":22,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"d648d61738","type":"paragraph","text":"34.97","index":23,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"88b4012202","type":"paragraph","text":"58.21669.56","index":24,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"296c3604c1","type":"paragraph","text":"61.92","index":25,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"efc8319ecc","type":"paragraph","text":"399.271976","index":26,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"b1a5e5f1de","type":"paragraph","text":"36.92","index":27,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"11642b0176","type":"paragraph","text":"59.63资料来源：《上海工运志》、《上海统计志》.1]由表一可见：1966—1976年的“文革”期间，上海的社会劳动者人数是逐年增长的，前五年增长80.11万人，后五年增长128.69万人，总共达208.8万人。再看职工人数（因本课题的主旨为城市社会生活史，所以在社会劳动者人数的具体统计中，就省略了“城镇个体劳动者”、“农村集体和个体劳动者”的数据，只展示在职职工的统计情况），前五年增长35.37万人，后五年增长91.77万人，总共达127.14万人。且从1970年始，社会劳动者人数超过了总人口的50%，即总人口中有一半进人了劳动年龄人口的行列（1976年时，该比例达到61.92%）。这主要是因为50年代生育高峰期的人口，每年以20万人以上的规模，从非在业状态转向在业状态。","index":28,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"aeac07348d","type":"paragraph","text":"为了进一步说明问题，请看表二","index":29,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"6624da5636","type":"paragraph","text":"表二1966—1976年上海市职工人数统计表"