rticleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"eba61d0cef","type":"paragraph","text":"（9.4）（0.3）（1.8）（0.2）","index":107,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"91623ec5bc","type":"paragraph","text":"（续表）农林运输商饮城市科教","index":108,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"53754d7dd7","type":"paragraph","text":"机关基本","index":109,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"9aa2290a00","type":"paragraph","text":"其他","index":110,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"5bbe4c5fa5","type":"paragraph","text":"金融","index":111,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"312f16a9af","type":"paragraph","text":"工业年份合计","index":112,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"b3aa0d3bab","type":"paragraph","text":"建设水气","index":113,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"0b9c47ab03","type":"paragraph","text":"邮电服供","index":114,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"70e0587526","type":"paragraph","text":"公用文卫（比例）（比例）（比例）","index":115,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"50aa4ad8b6","type":"paragraph","text":"团体（比例）（比例）（比例）（比例）（比例）（比例）（比例）（比例）","index":116,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"7e8ce5325c","type":"paragraph","text":"1.305.780.37203.0919.64","index":117,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"fb1f3aa115","type":"paragraph","text":"27.8524.5850.00","index":118,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"6e2bcc3fc2","type":"paragraph","text":"8.4935.431975376.53（53.9）5.2）（7.4）（6.5）（13.3）","index":119,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"c9348ec8c2","type":"paragraph","text":"（2.3）（9.4）（0.4）","index":120,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"4055e08620","type":"paragraph","text":"1.5）（0.1）","index":121,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"37b944c774","type":"paragraph","text":"26.1953.349.3437.671.395.910.34","index":122,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"0b5fbb6891","type":"paragraph","text":"209.7622.0233.311976399.2752.5（5.5（8.3）（6.6）（13.4）（2.3）","index":123,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"f3a09d99f7","type":"paragraph","text":"（9.4）（0.4）（1.5）（0.1）资料来源：《上海劳动志》由表四可知：","index":124,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"009a5322b0","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，从1965-1976年，在国民经济各部门中，除了机关团体人员减少了近1万人外-—这主要是“文革”运动通过“五·七”干校、千部下放“战高温”、“四个面向”等被逐渐驱逐的结果——其他各大口的职工人数均有所增长，例如工业系统增加61.72万人，商业服务系统增加11.16万人，科教文卫系统增加7.19万人等。固然，这与各大系统的基础有关，但终究证明了“文革”期间上海国民经济各部门仍处在扩大规模的状况中。选取工业和科教文卫系统作进一步的韵析，可发现“文革”十年间，全民所有制工矿企业的重工业部门增加了30.36万人（所占比例增长4.98%）；轻工业部门增加了10.39万人（增长0.99%）；纺织工业增加1.78万人（增长5.97%）。而教卫系统中的高等学校教师数量基本保持在1.1万人的规模，中学教师的数量则因入学人口膨胀净增了2.07万人，小学教师甚至出现负增长（-0.01万人）。16]看来，在国民经济各部门职业人口有所增长的背后，其内部或因产业结构的调整，或因人口变动的需求，而使在业人口的分布出现了新的变局。","index":125,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"9ae5bc7d5d","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，在职业总人口增长的前提下，深人观察上海“文革”十年间国民经济各部门职工人数占全市职工总数的比例，可发现比例有所提高的是基本建设、农林水气、运输邮电等三个部门。金融行业维持原有的比例。其余如工业、商饮服供、城市公用、科教文卫等部门均有不同程度的下降。在此，“农林水气”的职工比提高5.1%（职工数净增24.6万人），主要是因为市属18个农场（位于郊县15个，外地3个）先后吸纳了30多万的市区毕业生。虽然这属上山下乡的任务，但“农场职工”的身份，仍划人全民所有制企业的统计范之中。而“基本建设”、“运输邮电”的职工比上升，则应认为是上海经济在“文革”十年间，较注重“以工业为主导”的“基础”和“规模”的建设。反之，关系并直接有利于人们生活的商饮服供、城市公用、科教文卫等职工比均下降，应认为是当时上海的城市功能有所弱化。关于上海社会劳动者人数三次产业分布的统计可引为证验（如表五）。","index":126,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"a7e58f949c","type":"paragraph","text":"表五上海社会劳动者人数按三次产业分布统计表","index":127,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"71d6d03426","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：万人、%第一产业","index":128,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"23145faeb5","type":"paragraph","text":"第二产业","index":129,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"f566d8779c","type":"paragraph","text":"第三产业年份社会劳动者人数","index":130,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"e130e72555","type":"paragraph","text":"460.76","index":131,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"b7d783b705","type":"paragraph","text":"188.7040.95","index":132,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"ce08c24f90","type":"paragraph","text":"160.6834.87111.3824.1719651970","index":133,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"483d23299b","type":"paragraph","text":"540.87","index":134,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"fc74aeb2dc","type":"paragraph","text":"199.6536.91229.5942.43111.6320.64646.88","index":135,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"41af361a23","type":"paragraph","text":"237.0036.64","index":136,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"8513bc199c","type":"paragraph","text":"277.1942.85132.6920.5119751985","index":137,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"6aa09d61aa","type":"paragraph","text":"442.2757.93194.5025.47763.52","index":138,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"2f10574688","type":"paragraph","text":"126.7516.60资料来源：《上海统计志》。","index":139,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"5ff13d7ef2","type":"paragraph","text":"由表五所知，在整个*文革”期间，上海从事第一产业（农业）的人数比虽有所下降，终究因为幅度太小，仍保持在三分之一强的水准上。而“文革”结束以后的十年，该项人数和人数比才发生了大幅度的滑坠。与此同时，从事第二产业（工业和建筑业）的人数和人数比均持续上升，甚至达到二分之一弱。然而，恰怡是这第一产业人数比的些微下降和第二产业人数比的持续上升，挤迫并压缩着上海的第三产业，使第三产业的人数比从四分之一减少到五分之一","index":140,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"1ef74cc0a6","type":"paragraph","text":"其实，上海是集金融、贸易和生产功能于一体的综合性城市，历史上曾“第二产业强盛，第三产业发达”。造至解放初的1952年，上海第一、二、三次产业在全市国内生产总值中的构成比尚为5.9：52.4：41.7，与当时国际先进城市的差异不大。此后直至“文化大革命”结束后的1978年，因上海经济坚持“以发展工业为主体”（实为传统工业），第二产业的比重便从52.4%上升到77.4%；第三产业的比重则从41.7%下降到18.6%。如此严重的产业结构失调，终于使上海失去了金融、贸易等城市型经济功能，从一个综合型城市转变为生产型城市，并造成城市布局混乱、交通拥挤、工业区与居民区杂处等一系列影响人们生活的社会矛盾和困难。7在此，如果说50年代上海经济的发展路向，已决定上海城市的定位发生了功能性失误，那么，六七十年代伴随着政治需求的发展，更使这种失误走向了尽头。1978年以后，改革开放重建了上海经济发展战略，产业结构才得到调整，城市功能才得到恢复。","index":141,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"bd91596b6f","type":"paragraph","text":"四、职工分类和性别构成","index":142,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"80ef236155","type":"paragraph","text":"下面在职工队伍构成方面，选取“职工分类”和“性别结构”作简要闸述。先看表六。","index":143,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"5c817184fe","type":"paragraph","text":"表六若千年份上海市全民所有制工矿企业职工分类比例统计表","index":144,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"e8b6763c7a","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：万人、%","index":145,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"ad6d8d51ed","type":"paragraph","text":"学徒工人","index":146,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"2c5c732244","type":"paragraph","text":"管理人员服务人员其他人员","index":147,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"4f966f9baa","type":"paragraph","text":"技术人员年份总人数","index":148,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"1cd49d7a28","type":"paragraph","text":"（比例）（比例）（比例）","index":149,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"cbe8e9b653","type":"paragraph","text":"（比例）","index":150,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"2570e27783","type":"paragraph","text":"（比例）","index":151,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"88cb94bd94","type":"paragraph","text":"（比例）85.85","index":152,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"de3a727ecf","type":"paragraph","text":"6.33","index":153,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"f61ed5c208","type":"paragraph","text":"5.77","index":154,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"ea759f284d","type":"paragraph","text":"7.859.38","index":155,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"bccf8822da","type":"paragraph","text":"3.411965118.59","index":156,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"5a90797e7f","type":"paragraph","text":"（72.4）","index":157,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"35e396b1e3","type":"paragraph","text":"（5.3）","index":158,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"6d15316361","type":"paragraph","text":"（4.9）","index":159,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"e99e402221","type":"paragraph","text":"（7.9）","index":160,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"add11ba5ce","type":"paragraph","text":"（6.6）","index":161,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"530a2eca4d","type":"paragraph","text":"（2.9）115.29","index":162,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"c01fa13e79","type":"paragraph","text":"12.739.57","index":163,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"ae52d51c70","type":"paragraph","text":"13.50","index":164,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"0e63fdd343","type":"paragraph","text":"4.30","index":165,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"b098a0b543","type":"paragraph","text":"5.731976161.12","index":166,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"9746c44e79","type":"paragraph","text":"（71.6）","index":167,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"03de91710b","type":"paragraph","text":"（5.9）","index":168,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"5d145abc7f","type":"paragraph","text":"（3.6）","index":169,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"a16aa21f10","type":"paragraph","text":"（8.4）","index":170,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"c3d11da2ea","type":"paragraph","text":"（7.9）","index":171,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"4d55e9a841","type":"paragraph","text":"（2.6）资料来源：《上海劳动志》。","index":172,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"0eaf652a36","type":"paragraph","text":"由表六可知：从1965年到1976年，上海全民单位职工队伍中除技术人员的总人数、人数比均下降外，其余分类中“学徒”、“管理人员”和“服务人员”的总人数、人数比均上升。作为职工分类中主体存在的“工人”，则总人数有所增加，人数比却有些微的下降。这就是说在整个“文革”期间，上海全民单位的职工队伍不仅在数量上有所增加，且在管理和服务的岗位上（属非生产人员）有所增多。如果这仍属正常的变化，那么技术人员总人数、人数比均下降的事实，则应是违背企业管理规律的，属非正常的变化一而这怡恰是“文革”运动批判知识分子为“臭老九”，愉动“高贵者最悬，卑践者最聪明”等所导致的直接后果。纵观《上海劳动志》记载的该项统计（从1957-1990年），技术人员的总人数、人数比均年年增扩，只有“文革”这一段是四陷的。确实，这段四陷是孤独的，是触目的。然而也正是这一段从职业人口分类变化的角度，证实了“文革”运动排后技术人员，排斤技术进步的荒唐和不幸。","index":173,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"e4309c19b9","type":"paragraph","text":"关于职工队伍“性别结构”的统计可看表七：","index":174,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"fb82095a6c","type":"paragraph","text":"表七若干年份上海市女职工人数及比例统计表","index":175,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"9617f3e319","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：万人、%全民所有制","index":176,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"e6a204a2fd","type":"paragraph","text":"集体所有制职工","index":177,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"ddd81cb185","type":"paragraph","text":"女职工数年份","index":178,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"ac8e05e711","type":"paragraph","text":"总数","index":179,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"bee15717b4","type":"paragraph","text":"（比例）","index":180,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"69d03b743c","type":"paragraph","text":"职工总数女职工数（比例）职工总数女职工数（比例）104.90","index":181,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"424112cd62","type":"paragraph","text":"63.07","index":182,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"afffa3a9e2","type":"paragraph","text":"41.831965272.13","index":183,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"e12827e601","type":"paragraph","text":"212.37","index":184,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"8ca9349eea","type":"paragraph","text":"59.76（38.5）","index":185,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"118cd5150c","type":"paragraph","text":"（29.7）","index":186,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"162db03bfd","type":"paragraph","text":"（70.0）116.63","index":187,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"1dbfa6e888","type":"paragraph","text":"74.37","index":188,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"28f07bff15","type":"paragraph","text":"42.291970307.50","index":189,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"14025f9e8b","type":"paragraph","text":"244.53","index":190,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"ab479b9ee2","type":"paragraph","text":"62.97（37.9）","index":191,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"b4e9e6070c","type":"paragraph","text":"（30.4）","index":192,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"3be67a5fd1","type":"paragraph","text":"（67.2）158.47","index":193,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"c1fe4570c9","type":"paragraph","text":"103.43","index":194,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"288e595b11","type":"paragraph","text":"55.041975376.53","index":195,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"e40e2a470b","type":"paragraph","text":"293.84","index":196,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"b0bd9a7090","type":"paragraph","text":"82.69（42.1）","index":197,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"50937b4b07","type":"paragraph","text":"（35.2）","index":198,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"dc4dae8155","type":"paragraph","text":"（66.6）","index":199,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"244d88825f","type":"paragraph","text":"111.48168.80","index":200,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"89672ef320","type":"paragraph","text":"57.321976399.27","index":201,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"eb90204e54","type":"paragraph","text":"312.26","index":202,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"b5b1da6125","type":"paragraph","text":"87.01（42.3）","index":203,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"6a4b4ce675","type":"paragraph","text":"（35.7）","index":204,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"3faac27492","type":"paragraph","text":"（65.9）资料来源：《上海劳动志》。","index":205,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"69a9855673","type":"paragraph","text":"由表七可知，从1965年到1976年，上海女职工数随着总职工数的增长而增长（人数增长63.9万，总数达168.80万人；人数比增长3.8%，达到42.3%）。这说明在女性就业的问题上，或许源于“革命理念”的指导；或许出于社会的集体认同，“文革”期间的政策和做法因高度强调“性别平等”、“同工同”，是没有产生任何偏差和歧视的。从某种角度去闸说，这确也反映了“文革”的时代特征。再作进一步的观察，可发现全民所有制单位的女职工数、人数比呈现出大幅度直线上升的态势（人数增长48.41万，人数比增长6.0%）；而集体所有制单位的女职工数却增长缓慢（人数增长15.49万），人数比甚至出现了持续下滑的状态。","index":206,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"f7c387d476","type":"paragraph","text":"存在于其中的原因首先是“文革”十年间，全民单位（含国营农场）大规模地从中学毕业生中吸纳职工。集体单位则因“所有制”方面的问题，至少在1968年大批“老三届”进入工矿时，没有被有关计划指令打开门户。以致“文革”前五年，上海集体单位的女职工数只增长了0.46万人。直到“一片红”的上山下乡政策被废弃后，集体单位才开始按照“一工一农”的分配原则接收毕业生。何况，在“文革”时代的社会集体认同中，每宁说集体所有制总有被割“资本主义尾巴”之嫌，它的单位的性质定位也就天然地低人一等（伴随着的“身份认同”也就低人一等）；就是集体所有制单位的规模（多为区属小企业及商业饮食服务单位）、福利等也是无法与全民单位比拟的。所以，不论是分配者还是被分配者，面对集体所有制的单位，总是有些无奈的。这应是集体单位女职工数相对增长缓慢的社会心理因素。","index":207,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"16db0a58f2","type":"paragraph","text":"其次关于女职工人数比的问题，应看到集体所有制单位在开创时期，存在着“解放妇女”的时代需要，所以集体单位的女职工人数比甚至高达85.0%（1957—1960），文革”运动开始前的1965年也高达70%。反之，全民所有制单位的女职工人数比在1965年前就没有超过30%，直至1970年才到达30.4%。其实，正是这种由历史形成的原初状态的人数比差异，才构成了表七中的数据分布和走向。这就是说它并不证明“文革”十年间全民单位偏重于吸纳女职工，而恰怡证明两者对此是同样采取自然态度的。所以，由于全民单位女职工基础人数和基础人数比均低，吸纳大量职工后，无疑人数和人数比均上升。而集体单位职工总数少，女职工人数比却很高，接受分配的新职工后，无疑职工总数上升，女职工人数比下降。总之，这也从一个侧面证实，“文革”期间强调以阶级“差异”消灭其他各种“差异”的社会思潮，在对待“性别差异”的问题上，确是没有任何比较和选择的。","index":208,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"28d7249688","type":"paragraph","text":"另外，具体察看“文革”期间女职工人数在国民经济客部门中的比例关系，可见“科教文卫”系统是始终排列首位的，例如其1965年时在全民单位所占比例就达43.3%，1976年时达到47.5%。“金融”系统的女职工人数比也很高，1976年的统计比例为33.6%。相反，“基本建设”和“运输邮电”系统的女职工人数比一直较低。8]这主要因为各行业对女性工作的适宜性要求是不同的，所以有关分配部门便“确定一定的男女比例，基本上运用行政手段，解决青年就业中的男女平衡问题”，9]以达到合乎常规性分布的目的，在此就不费述了。注释[1]李家齐：《上海工运志》，上海社会科学院出版社1997年版，第350页。颜德纶：","index":209,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"},{"id":"609c474d66","type":"paragraph","text":"《上海统计志》，上海社会科学院出版社1997年版，第283页。[2]沈智：《上海劳动志》，上海社会科学院出版社1998年版，第128页。[3]祝兆松：《上海计划志》，上海社会科学院出版社2001年版，第336页。L4]沈智：《上海劳动志》，上海社会科学院出版社1998年版，第174页。5]同上书，第174页。[6]李家齐：《上海工运志》，上海社会科学院出版社1997年版，第358-362页。[7熊月之：《上海通史》第十二卷，上海人民出版社1999年版，第330-333页。[8]沈智：《上海劳动志》，上海社会科学院出版社1998年版，第138页。[9]同上书，第79页。","index":210,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7"}],"page":{"id":"d3da368e41","publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"a59a7c68f7","start":71,"end":83}}}},"__N_SSG":true}